track.name: I Could Be The One (Avicii Vs. Nicky Romero) - Radio Edit

wiki.summary: This song was released under various names such as Nicktim, Fuck School, and Stranger, along with many others before it was officially released. The song is a collaboration between Swedish DJ Avicii (Tim Bergling) and Dutch DJ Nicky Romero (Nick Rotteveel). The song has uncredited vocals from Swedish singer Noonie Bao. The single became both DJ’s first UK chart topping song beating out the ever popular Harlem Shake by Baauer. The song has two different spectrum’s of the EDM scale colliding resulting in a catchy feel good track. Read more on Last.fm.
